{"tid":155234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張超雄：過份渲染對南亞人不公","createTime":"2017-03-14T00:36:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-19T14:10:50.000Z","uid":28435,"like":3,"dislike":78,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e8b07839c22d365132b333214739b6d66484a0c3","tid":155234,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T00:36:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170314/large/17800413.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170314%2Flarge%2F17800413.jpg&h=e00185ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【本報訊】近期接連發生涉及南亞裔人士的案件，惹輿論關注現行免遣反聲請機制，是否造就罪案上升的原因。不過有議員及關注團體認為不能一竹篙打一船人，擔心過份渲染南亞裔人士犯罪的事件，會對南亞裔人士不公道，更令本地少數族裔難以融入社會。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n非華裔被捕者增5.1%<br />\n據警方數字，去年非華裔人士因刑事罪行被捕人數有4,703人，較前年增加5.1%，佔整體被捕人數14.1%，比例較前年增加0.8個百分點。被捕4,703非華裔人士中，香港居民及非居民各佔約半，其中持行街紙的非華裔犯案人數達1,506人，較前年增加393人，升幅達35%。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170314/large/a0604a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170314%2Flarge%2Fa0604a.gif&h=c4e52d10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會議員張超雄不諱言，涉及持行街紙南亞裔人士的案件確實不少，但是否佔罪案比例特別多，值得深究，警方應具體掌握有關情況，並向公眾解釋。他擔心社會過份渲染有關問題，會構成歧視及分化問題，「好似講親南亞裔人士就同罪案有關，咁係唔公道，亦影響少數族裔融入社會嘅機會」。<br />\n融樂會總幹事張鳳美亦質疑南亞人士持行街紙，不等同會導致罪案上升，兩者未必有必然關係。她亦擔心過份渲染有關問題，一竹篙打一船人，會加深市民對南亞裔人士的誤解。她又指有關問題自立法會選舉以來都已變得相當政治化，呼籲市民勿以有色眼鏡看待南亞裔人士。<br />\n對於有意見認為應再新設立禁閉營，關注難民權益組織「Justice Centre Hong Kong」研究及政策主任李敏指出，外國經驗顯示設立禁閉營所花費的社會資源及費用更多，而從個人基本權利的角度而言亦違反人權，故該會反對有關建議。<br />\n■記者劉柏麟"},{"pid":"9c582b7f7a3cb94f2fbe1a78569cefa275206dd4","tid":155234,"uid":67485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T00:37:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bff09b43835d94c9b143d516376da40df0a4885a","tid":155234,"uid":11261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T00:38:39.000Z","msg":"唔怪得個女係弱智<br />\n盡得老豆遣傳"},{"pid":"ba54e70bd8a4df46fbb779b4ef9debe526c6d479","tid":155234,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T00:39:12.000Z","msg":"咁低等人種天生就應該俾人歧視架啦<br />\n有咩好講"},{"pid":"6e790dcdd979d12214a96ea6f63f65193c1297cd","tid":155234,"uid":60137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T00:41:07.000Z","msg":"遲早買槍返黎打死呢條仆街"},{"pid":"e9c54ed2441eac082b42b4a8e37a769d78901fdc","tid":155234,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T00:43:53.000Z","msg":"呢d垃圾根本唔應該自由活動<br />\n應該起間集中營困住佢地<br />\n之後查明身分就逐批趕佢地出境<br />\n比假資料，有案低既就直接處決啦屌"},{"pid":"3e05fbccbf173d5fa934cd0079895f55e01c648b","tid":155234,"uid":21249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T00:46:18.000Z","msg":"南亞之父張banner真係無屌錯佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f483f7a28c946745f2ab1aa5f65b103ac445da50","tid":155234,"uid":2974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T00:47:42.000Z","msg":"以為自己係X教授呀屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b48e6d463dd5883c0567343e7bef4bd025c1e9","tid":155234,"uid":33077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T00:52:24.000Z","msg":"咁有無d正面例子佢可以提出黎？<br />\n我眼見既南亞人<br />\n隨街吐口水<br />\n有次去商場配眼鏡期間有3～4個南亞細路入左黎拎晒眼鏡鋪俾客擺出黎個d糖即刻轉頭走<br />\n個老細嘆氣一聲我覺得好無奈<br />\nd糖係擺向度俾人食唔收錢<br />\n但無幫襯之餘就拎晒<br />\n<br />\n我明人不分人種都有好壞<br />\n但唔管制既話對無做壞事既南亞人都係唔公平"},{"pid":"28439e798b8844914324513adf65ef5fe91ebfee","tid":155234,"uid":3860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T00:58:29.000Z","msg":"又賴選舉<br />\n立法會都選完十世 咪又係個個屌"},{"pid":"8c0610ca5e1c61aad4e42e363ffdeaec509fe200","tid":155234,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T01:03:07.000Z","msg":"又係你條撚屌難民之父，含家剷顧掂自己個女先啦"},{"pid":"37d05148dd8cec84892741745612d9d945fa4174","tid":155234,"uid":18959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T01:04:18.000Z","msg":"2年就升左差唔多個double<br />\n咁你都講得出不公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e1095e2185aca48c5f00ef0ac0dc6f9dd1f6d8","tid":155234,"uid":34468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T01:08:27.000Z","msg":"佔整體14%都幾誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f8a52849c607da1eb4697800f4ba09928ecdd48","tid":155234,"uid":52283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T01:16:28.000Z","msg":"屌你老母張超雄，又話支那人來拿福利，又係咁叫D蝻入香港"},{"pid":"e78b7c047905e03741303f312d6299b142ae7c16","tid":155234,"uid":7790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T01:35:00.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母"},{"pid":"25e51b555f37f749ce61980ee43830f38e41c390","tid":155234,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T01:39:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佔整體14%都幾誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但佢地人數係佔香港人比率係低"},{"pid":"a89599f0b03560879c4ad1f2e9c8cc8cc474fd2f","tid":155234,"uid":52824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T01:40:39.000Z","msg":"你老母比狗屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40d21b93e1a4c9c7fe572b171320a660ee5ea7cb","tid":155234,"uid":17928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T01:42:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔怪得個女係弱智<br />\n盡得老豆遣傳</blockquote><br />\n你好撚賤<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但我同樣咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a11dabd742b330cf38e6b22d6181431b33d210a","tid":155234,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T01:48:51.000Z","msg":"張鳳美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n油麻地發生警員開槍案，融樂會總幹事張鳳美說，警方是否一定要在當時開槍，交由警方去評論，她們關心的是警方在開槍之前，有沒有足夠的溝通，向對方說現時有一個警告，如果警方察覺到對方不是一名華裔人士，應該用英語及雙語去警告。<br />\n<br />\n張鳳美希望警方應該反映或反省一下，香港是一個兩文三語的地方，如果每次都是用廣東話作出口頭警告，是否足夠。<br />\n<br />\n上年南亞劈緊人個陣話差佬冇用雙語警告先開槍<br />\n<br />\n比人屌到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c00925ed0df07b966e53682504defcfe0a555ca2","tid":155234,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T01:55:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佔整體14%都幾誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但佢地人數係佔香港人比率係低</blockquote><br />\n我意思係 比率低可以佔咁高整體 畀人當全部都係潛在罪犯不為過"},{"pid":"87ade9e377dac51cd01e22d2b6ab8bf590278c94","tid":155234,"uid":75870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T01:56:54.000Z","msg":"賣港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f8cccb99facba361a653a2cc4cec039639614f0","tid":155234,"uid":60020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T01:57:41.000Z","msg":"送哂去張超雄屋企喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43027e4ffe5d49e0b8564b82923a832faa22fc16","tid":155234,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T02:08:11.000Z","msg":"邏輯上應該係南亞人唔犯罪就無人報囉<br />\n<br />\n唔通你想好似北歐咁連難民強姦金毛一線鮑都唔可以講咩<br />\n<br />\n不如你做下野減輕佢地犯罪率好過啦"},{"pid":"141100cb766e8b75c4de7a01adfc25a77a47c1e2","tid":155234,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T02:21:04.000Z","msg":"屌你捐撚晒全副身家同間屋養佢地啦"},{"pid":"5f2c78c25408e65c2c4f4aab7e6348f27908a1d3","tid":155234,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T02:27:35.000Z","msg":"根據張超雄既邏輯，蝻亞人既犯罪率一日未到100%，你都唔可以屌啲蝻亞人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ef0d0a34ee5e8a5d8d1b06212ea3bcba1291808","tid":155234,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T02:30:36.000Z","msg":"多謝張超雄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/oq7k9wn1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Foq7k9wn1&h=acd91448&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c7535c0212c6846d00271dd48d6ea204a395b89","tid":155234,"uid":70689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T02:32:36.000Z","msg":"咁邊個對香港人公平呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b0964aae001b354811cf9f9abae5180581bdae","tid":155234,"uid":91325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T02:37:34.000Z","msg":"呢d大愛撚真係累撚死人"},{"pid":"f960fa250dc6c714fca76c280cc90cd701279d94","tid":155234,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T02:42:33.000Z","msg":"咩叫過份渲染？？<br />\n報導事實都叫過份渲染！<br />\n而家有南亞人成日犯法， 傳媒報導， 市民擔心理所當然， 有咩過唔過份<br />\n我睇唔到點過份渲染"},{"pid":"5da986b5d0ed7f74f29e3895d76e6d3c58c309aa","tid":155234,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T02:44:16.000Z","msg":"UST蝻亞狗入黎吠兩聲先啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a8205efd10bf531118c4bf180d8c4b4aff8a3aa","tid":155234,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T02:46:42.000Z","msg":"其實呢班人成撚日護住佢哋做乜<br />\n我就當佢唔犯法咁佢哋對香港有咩貢獻？？<br />\n比咁多入嚟做乜撚嘢， 有咩益處"},{"pid":"b8146bb3b9f5a4d063cee5e456cff36db6b89c1d","tid":155234,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T02:51:06.000Z","msg":"佢邏輯係報紙作新聞<br />\n<br />\n仲有 果堆所謂難民99%以上聲請無效<br />\n邊撚度難呀屌"},{"pid":"3ba8fb27653532adbc492259156c8fbaeecf18d2","tid":155234,"uid":32723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"